				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just buy the elem fire spell at 4th lvl since it'll be basically all you'll be using as these elems have generally more hp, do higher dmg, and a couple more lvls higher than a normal elem summoned.  Just tank for it while it dishes out damage, while this is suicidal for mages after awhile, it is considered a good tactic at lower lvls.  Also while tempting when you get some money together to buy every spell and have them all, it isn't the wisest choice since most of your spells cost like 5 pp at 8th lvl and you want to have enough for the damage shield, your shield, and one elemental at least by then.
